list.name: Default Changelist
list.comment: time class was added in WorldState. WorldState can be package with two non-static classes for time and for weather, but I want have a static classes for change time and weather. TimeController in WorldState have nested class, which can be extended in PhysicalObject class (and child) All who extends ObjectTimeController can override function updateThis(). This function are called by ObjectTimeController from another objects when time are changed. You can change some fields there (which logical connecting with time) also rename field "state" in Food class to "foodState" (yea, this changes, not extending, but I think it will be more friendly to use)
